// 5) shouldComponentUpdate life cycle method
// Ye puchta ha k component ko update karna ha ya nae jese hum ne koe state change karwae to render method ya kise bhi life cycle method ko update karna ha ya nae ye hum condition mei bta sakte.
// Hum specific condition deker stop karwa sakte k render method ab na update ho jese state 4 bar pe render update ho us ke bad nae
// By default ye method component to update nae hone deta wo block kar deta ha jese hum click kar rhe state update console mei dikh rhe per output mei 0 he ha to jab hum return true karengy wo upadte hone dega. wo show es liye nahi hota kiyu k render method dobara chala he nae es ne update hone he nae dia.
// Hum condition bhi laga sakte k srf  5 or 10 ke bech mei show ho render method update ho wese nahi ho
// componentDidUpdate es ke bad call hota ha because ye decide karta tha render update hoga ya nae ek bar render update hwe to componentDidUpdate call hojaega.

/*
